Title: Ep. 18 - Autotune, Inclusivity, and Getting A Job (Vanessa Hurst)
Description: Vanessa Hurst, founder of CodeMontage, has spent a lot of her career making tech an inclusive space for all people, particularly women. We talk about how she created that space through Girl Develop It, the non-profit she founded, her perspective on managing your career as a code newbie, and particularly about getting that first tech job.
